{"tid":1171713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反對《逃犯條例》修訂 向美國白宮遞交聯署","createTime":"2019-05-26T02:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T02:02:17.000Z","uid":185066,"like":64,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b768f3adc17e782445a0ac56af7991b104268e0f","tid":1171713,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:15:02.000Z","msg":"一齊推埋白宮出聲啦 無論你地覺得有冇用 一人一簽名都可以積少成多 如果你地有心關注香港既未來 就唔好怕花一分鐘入去簽一簽個名<br />\n<br />\n【聯署】<br />\n*反對《逃犯條例》修訂，向美國白宮遞交聯署*，如人數達10萬，白宮就必須回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFEUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=36592ef7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a><br />\n<br />\n請聯署及廣傳🙏🏻"},{"pid":"43cdb55fe05be3ef2658e07197f8a546a3294da8","tid":1171713,"uid":149026,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:15:57.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"658c980fd750f377b785e6ad9309c3651ab492dd","tid":1171713,"uid":31749,"like":2,"dislike":74,"score":-72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed6afcf40c905fd38fc1ee4eb6fa433df5e7a2ee","tid":1171713,"uid":178187,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"658c980fd750f377b785e6ad9309c3651ab492dd","tid":1171713,"uid":31749,"like":2,"dislike":74,"score":-72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:16:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:22:45.000Z","msg":"十足十啲廢老語氣<br />\n<br />\n咁香港事關中國咩事啊？啊爺咪又照插手<br />\n<br />\n修例影響埋外資對香港既信心，咁依家仲關唔關事啊？<br />\n<br />\n三毛死撚開啦"},{"pid":"3d58de07aa7d37f78c1dea6d8e57dd